(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

The purpose of these regulations is to revoke the Commercial Vehicle 
Roadworthiness (Vehicle Licensing) Regulations 2014 (S.I. No. 397 of 2014).
